http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Interview-for-people-with-disabilities/article14022709.ece

The Bengaluru-based Prarthanam Angavikalara Samsthe and Department of Empowerment of People with Disabilities and Senior Citizens have planned to conduct direct interview for recruitment of handicapped people on January 29.The interview will be held on the premises of the District Employment Office from 10.30 a.m. to 4 p.m., District Employment Officer K.V. Ashwathnarayan said in a release.Contact 98804 91392 or 98451 39255 for details.